

## 🌍 General Awareness

### **Topic: Inventions & Discoveries (VERY IMPORTANT 🔥)**

---

# 1️⃣ Clear Theory (Easy Language)

An **Invention** is creating something new.

A **Discovery** is finding something that already existed.

📌 Examples:

* Telephone → Invention
* Gravity → Discovery

---

# 2️⃣ Important Inventions

| Invention  | Inventor              |
| ---------- | --------------------- |
| Telephone  | Alexander Graham Bell |
| Light Bulb | Thomas Edison         |
| Aeroplane  | Wright Brothers       |
| Television | John Logie Baird      |
| Computer   | Charles Babbage       |

---

# 3️⃣ Important Discoveries

| Discovery     | Scientist         |
| ------------- | ----------------- |
| Gravity       | Isaac Newton      |
| Penicillin    | Alexander Fleming |
| Radioactivity | Henri Becquerel   |
| Electron      | J.J. Thomson      |
| X-Rays        | Wilhelm Röntgen   |

---

